      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>A type of qǝne composed of two strophes, the total consisting of
               seven or eleven verses, sung during the Communion. This is a general record, to be used when 
               the qǝne type is known but the text is inaccessible.</p>
         </abstract>
